title: How to load letter paper into the Brother MFC-J5830DW
description:
Learn how to load letter paper into your Brother MFC-J5330DW, MFC-J5830DW, or MFC-J5930DW inkjet all-in-one.

The model shown is the MFC-J5830DW

Models covered:
Brother MFCJ5330DW inkjet all-in-one
Brother MFCJ5830DW inkjet all-in-one
Brother MFCJ5930DW inkjet all-in-one

For more videos, tutorials, and FAQs visit our support site at: http://www.brother-usa.com/support
